data.description: Enjoy the Villas at Hershey Meadows in South Hanover Twp! Reduce your responsibility without having to give up living space and comforts. More than 2,400 square feet of living space. Spacious floor plan, family room with gas fireplace, living room, dining area and open kitchen with microwave range hood and all appliances included. Spacious owner's suite with whirlpool tub, shower, double bowl vanity and large walk-in closet with organizers. Jack and Jill bath connects the second and third bedrooms also with a double bowl sink. Premium lot with rear patio and backs to undeveloped area for added privacy. Convenient two car garage, new flooring, new HVAC system and hot water heater. Located just minutes from Hershey Medical Center and I-81. Affordable and convenient, come see it today!
